to initialize package.json = npm init -y
to initialize tsconfig.json =- tsc --init

 "scripts": {
    "start:build":"tsc -w",
    "start:run":"nodemon build/index.js",
    "start":"concurrently npm:start:*"
  },

  inside this tag you can give as start:typescript or anything you like instead of start:build
  same is applicable for start:run
  but not applicable for start --  it must be as start only.